OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry start with just
OL,6,Fthe odd shower around. A bright but
OL,7,Frather cloudy day with showers
OL,8,Fdeveloping more widely from late
OL,9,Fmorning onwards, some heavy and
OL,10,Fthundery.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome heavy and thundery
OL,13,Fshowers at first, these slowly dying
OL,14,Fout during the evening. A dry night
OL,15,Fwith clear spells and becoming rather
OL,16,Fchilly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
